                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On September 11, 1950, Secretary of State Acheson discussed the world situation
                    in executive session before the Senate Foreign Relations Committee; for the
                    record of his testimony, see <hi rend="italic">Reviews of the <pb facs="0414"
                            n="398" xml:id="pg_398"/> World Situation, 1949–1950: Hearings Held in
                        Executive Session Before the Committee on Foreign Relations, United States
                        Senate</hi> (81st Cong., 1st and 2nd sessions), pages 339–366.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
